B. Commission System Testing (CRITICAL):

âœ… Scenario 1: Client Direct Order (No Referral)

  1. Client registers without referral link
  2. Client creates order (Rp 5,000,000)
  3. Client uploads payment proof
  4. Admin approves payment
  5. Expected: Order marked paid, NO commission
  6. âœ“ PASS / âœ— FAIL

âœ… Scenario 2: Client via Partner Referral (Tier 2)

  1. Client registers via Partner A referral link
  2. Partner A is Tier 2 (40% commission)
  3. Client orders Rp 5,000,000
  4. Admin approves payment
  5. Expected:
     - Order marked paid
     - Partner A commission: Rp 2,000,000 (40%)
     - Email sent to Partner A
  6. âœ“ PASS / âœ— FAIL

âœ… Scenario 3: Commission Cascade (Partner â†’ SPV â†’ Manager)

  1. Partner B (Tier 2, 40%) has SPV C
  2. SPV C has Manager D
  3. Client orders Rp 10,000,000 via Partner B referral
  4. Admin approves payment
  5. Expected:
     - Partner B: Rp 4,000,000 (40%)
     - SPV C: Rp 1,000,000 (10%)
     - Manager D: Rp 500,000 (5%)
     - SITUNEO: Rp 4,500,000 (45%)
     - Emails sent to all three
  6. âœ“ PASS / âœ— FAIL

âœ… Scenario 4: Subscription Stop <3 Months (Auto-Deduct)

  1. Client subscribes Rp 1,500,000/month via Partner E
  2. Partner E earns Rp 600,000 commission (Tier 2, 40%)
  3. Client cancels after 2 months (before 3 months)
  4. Cron job runs daily check
  5. Expected:
     - Partner E balance deducted -Rp 600,000
     - If Partner E has SPV: SPV gets Rp 60,000 (10%)
     - If SPV has Manager: Manager gets Rp 30,000 (5%)
     - Partner E loses Rp 510,000 net
     - Email sent to Partner E
  6. âœ“ PASS / âœ— FAIL

âœ… Scenario 5: Partner Tier Upgrade (Maintenance)

  1. Partner F has 8 orders (Tier 1, 30%)
  2. Partner F gets 5 more orders (total 13)
  3. System checks tier (monthly cron)
  4. Expected:
     - Partner F upgraded to Tier 2 (40%)
     - Next month, Partner F has only 8 orders
     - Tier STAYS at Tier 2 (maintenance rule)
     - Tier never decreases
  5. âœ“ PASS / âœ— FAIL

âœ… Scenario 6: SPV Bonus (ARPU Calculation)

  1. SPV G has 10 downline partners
  2. Total revenue from downlines: Rp 350,000,000
  3. ARPU = Rp 350,000,000 / 10 = Rp 35,000,000
  4. Monthly cron calculates ARPU
  5. Expected:
     - ARPU Rp 35,000,000 = Tier 2
     - SPV G bonus: Rp 1,000,000
     - Bonus added to balance
     - Email sent
  6. âœ“ PASS / âœ— FAIL

âœ… Scenario 7: Job Late Delivery Penalty

  1. Partner H accepts job (Rp 5,000,000, 14 days deadline)
